      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KEAYANG TWEETYBIRD (5) added to her recent string of strong performances last time out when runner-up over 2200m at Ballarat, beaten 2.75 metres. Meets a comparable field so she can go one better this time around. SIR EROS (9) has had two runs this campaign and is yet to finish in the top three. Was again unable to find the frame last start when he finished eighth over 1720m at Melton, beaten 125 metres. Finds a nice race and can improve sharply. SONARMI JOH (7) is a consistent performer with three top-three finishes on the trot. Only needs things to fall his way and the good recent form can convert to a well-deserved win. SOSO MAJESTIC (6) has been about the mark of late and must be respected, the latest offering a sound fifth at Bendigo over 2150m.",
